  <scopecontent id="aspace_c25030544ffc8435830c5479127ed623">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Includes 7 volumes of copies of deeds showing trackage locations (1868-1912); 48 volumes of dispatchers' diaries used at Norwich and noting the weather, accidents, and unusual occurrences on the Northern Division (1890-1893, 1896, 1898-1940); 19 volumes of engineers' survey books (c. 1910), which give specifications for improvements in track and structures; official notices of schedule and route changes (1948-1956); map and survey; timetable (1954); map and profile of the Pecksport Loop line. Chenango County, Madison County, Oneida County, Oswego County.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <prefercite id="aspace_56a54df64c3b2c9ed0ccea7c65a42ccd">
    <head>Cite As:</head>
<p>New York, Ontario, &amp; Western Railway Co. records, #1949. Division of Rare and Manuscript Collections, Cornell University Library.</p>  </prefercite>
